Waltz With Bashir;;91;;96;;R;;Israeli filmmaker Ari Folman wrote, directed and stars in this autobiographical animated film. As a 19-year-old infantry soldier in the 1982 war with Lebanon, Folman witnessed the Sabra and Shatila massacre, but realizes that he has no memory of the event. In 2006, he seeks out others who were in Beirut at the time to discuss their memories, including a psychologist specializing in post-traumatic stress disorders and the first journalist to cover the massacre.;;Animation,Documentary;;Ari Folman;;2008;;Ron Ben-Yishai,Ronny Dayag,Ari Folman,Dror Harazi,Yehezkel Lazarov,Mickey Leon;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/waltz_with_bashir